1/mads-mikkelsen-replace-johnny-depp-fantastic-beasts-3-1234598075/ |archive-date=2020-11-24 |access-date=2020-11-25 |website=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |last=Rubin |first=Rebecca |date=2020-11-06 |title=Johnny Depp Forced to Exit 'Fantastic Beasts' Franchise |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/johnny-depp-exhits-fantastic-beasts-franchise-1234824564/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106162655/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/johnny-depp-exhits-fantastic-beasts-franchise-1234824564/ |archive-date=2020-11-06 |access-date=2020-11-26 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]}}</ref><ref name="ElPais 2 April 2022">{{cite web |last= Palacios |first=Iñigo López |title=Mads Mikkelsen, al rescate de 'Harry Potter': "Tomé el relevo de Johnny Depp porque era una emergencia, pero dudé" |language=es |trans-title=Mads Mikkelsen, to the rescue of 'Harry Potter': "I took over from Johnny Depp because it was an emergency, but I hesitated" |work=[[El_País|El País]] |publisher= |date=2022-04-02 |url=https://elpais.com/icon/2022-04-02/mads-mikkelsen-al-rescate-de-harry-potter-tome-el-relevo-de-johnny-depp-porque-era-una-emergencia-pero-dude.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220411174315/https://elpais.com/icon/2022-04-02/mads-mikkelsen-al-rescate-de-harry-potter-tome-el-relevo-de-johnny-depp-porque-era-una-emergencia-pero-dude.html |archive-date=2022-04-11 |url-status=live |access-date=2022-04-11}}</ref>。米基辛選擇不仿效特普的演譯，他在一次訪談中表示這將是「創造性自殺」，但承認仍然需要「在之前所發生的事物之間築起某種橋樑<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-04-14 |last=Hibberd |first=James |title=Mads Mikkelsen on 'Fantastic Beasts' Casting Chaos, Johnny Depp, JK Rowling and 'Indy 5' |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-features/mads-mikkelsen-interview-fantastic-beasts-johnny-depp-jk-rowling-1235129001/ |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=2022-04-16 |archive-date=2022-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416000253/https