[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]最初定於2019年7月開始進行，然而在2019年1月，由於《[[怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行|怪獸與葛林戴華德的罪行]]》的票房沒預期的多，華納兄弟宣佈為了有更多的時間完善劇本以及計劃好未來的電影，製作被推遲至2019年末<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/fantastic-beasts-3-pushes-production-start-to-late-fall-1202537147/|title=‘Fantastic Beasts 3’ Pushes Production Start To Late Fall|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-01-18|accessdate=2019-01-18|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119020556/https://deadline.com/2019/01/fantastic-beasts-3-pushes-production-start-to-late-fall-1202537147/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年10月，[[丹·富樂|丹·富樂]]聲稱第三部電影的主體拍攝將於2020年2月開始<ref>{{cite web|last=Marc|first=Christopher|url=https://hnentertainment.co/dan-fogler-says-fantastic-beasts-3-begins-filming-in-february/|title=Dan Fogler Says ‘Fantastic Beasts 3’ Begins Filming In February|publisher=HNEntertainment|date=2019-10-20|accessdate=2019-10-22|archive-date=2019-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191022153755/https://hnentertainment.co/dan-fogler-says-fantastic-beasts-3-begins-filming-in-february/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

主體拍攝原定於2020年3月16日開始，但礙於[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]影響，華納兄弟推遲了電影的製作<ref name="FantasticBeasts3FilmingPostponed">{{Cite web |last=D'Alessandro |first=Anthony |date=2020-03-15 |title='Fantastic Beasts 3' & 'King Richard' Warner Bros. Productions Are Also On Hiatus: Coronavirus |url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/fantastic-beasts-3-king-richard-warner-bros-movie-productions-halt-coronavirus-1202884003/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626142133/https://deadline.com/2020/03/fantastic-beasts-3-king-richard-warner-bros-movie-productions-halt-coronavirus-1202884003/ |archive-date=2020-06-26 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/fantastic-beasts-3-production-postponed-coronavirus-1203535480/|title=‘Fantastic Beasts 3’ Production Postponed Due to Coronavirus Pandemic|publisher=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2020-03-16|accessdate=2020-09-12|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813222117/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/fantastic-beasts-3-production-postponed-coronavirus-1203535480/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年8月20日，電影獲確認將於9月在[[英國|英國]]開始拍攝<ref>{{cite web|last=Hurwitz|first=Cassie|url=https://screenrant.com/fantastic-beasts-3-production-filming-september-update/|title=Fantastic Beasts 3 To Start Filming Next Month|publisher=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2020-08-20|accessdate=2020-09-12|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921135115/https://screenrant.com/fantastic-beasts-3-production-filming-september-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拍攝於9月20日正式開始，並採取了安全預防措施，以確保演員和工作人員免受COVID-19的傷害<ref name="FantasticBeasts3_resumes">{{Cite web |last=Webb |first=Katherine |date=2020-09-20 |title=Eddie Redmayne Confirms Fantastic Beasts 3 Filming Has Resumed And Describes The 'New Normal' On Set |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921135115/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set |archive-date=2020-09-21 |access-date=2020-09-20 |website=CinemaBlend}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |last=Siegel |first=Tatiana |date=2020-11-09 |title=Behind Warner Bros.' Decision to Sever Ties With Johnny Depp |work=The Hollywood Reporter |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/behind-warner-bros-decision-to-sever-ties-with-johnny-depp |url-status=live |access-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111163229/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/behind-warner-bros-decision-to-sever-ties-with-johnny-depp |archive-date=2020-11-11}}</ref>。同日，烈明尼證實電影經已開始拍攝<ref>{{cite web|last=Webb|first=Katherine|url=https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set?pv=related_list|title=Eddie Redmayne Confirms Fantastic Beasts 3 Filming Has Resumed And Describes The ‘New Normal’ On Set|publisher=CinemaBlend|date=2020-09-20|accessdate=2020-09-21|archive-date=2020-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200921135115/https://www.cinemablend.com/news/2555115/eddie-redmayne-confirms-fantastic-beasts-3-filming-has-resumed-and-describes-the-new-normal-on-set?pv=related_list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年2月3日，在一名工作人員的COVID-19檢測呈陽性後，在英國[[華納兄弟利維斯登工作室|華納兄弟利維斯登工作室]]的拍攝工作被暫停<ref>{{Cite web |last=Grater |first=Tom |date=2021-02-04 |title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Pauses UK Production After Positive Covid Test |url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/fantastic-beasts-3-pauses-uk-production-positive-covid-test-1234687188/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205083237/https://deadline.com/2021/02/fantastic-beasts-3-pauses-uk-production-positive-covid-test-1234687188/ |archive-date=2021-02-05 |access-date=2021-02-04 |website=Deadline Hollywood}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Ritman |first=Alex |date=2021-02-04 |title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Stops Shoot After Positive COVID Test |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fantastic-beasts-3-suspends-filming-positive-covid-test |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204134410/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fantastic-beasts-3-suspends-filming-positive-covid-test |archive-date=2021-02-04 |access-date=2021-02-04 |website=The Hollywood Reporter}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Ramachandran |first=Naman |author-link=Naman Ramachandran |date=2021-02-04 |title=Warner Bros. Suspends 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Shoot After Crew Member Tests Positive For COVID-19 |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/global/fantastic-beasts-3-suspended-covid-1234900398/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204101258/https://variety.com/2021/film/global/fantastic-beasts-3-suspended-covid-1234900398/ |archive-date=2021-02-04 |access-date=2021-02-04 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]}}</ref>。雖然這部電影以柏林和不丹為背景，但並非在真實地點拍攝。它們在利夫斯登華納兄弟工作室的廣闊外景和攝影棚中被重新構想和重建<ref>{{Cite web |last=Sharma |first=Dhruv |date=2022-04-15 |title=Where Was Fantastic Beasts 3 Filmed? All Wizarding World Locations |url=https://screenrant.com/where-was-fantastic-beasts-secrets-dumbledore-movie-filmed/ |website=Screenrant |access-date=2022-04-23 |archive-date=2022-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220423133857/https://screenrant.com/where-was-fantastic-beasts-secrets-dumbledore-movie-filmed/ }}</ref>。

作曲[[詹姆斯·紐頓·霍華|占士·紐頓·侯活]]在該月稍後時候證實，製作經已結束拍攝<ref>{{Cite web |last=Grober |first=Matt |date=2021-02-26 |title=Composer James Newton Howard on Penning 'News of the World's "Broken" Western Score & Returning to Disney Animation with 'Raya and the Last Dragon |url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/news-of-the-world-composer-james-newton-howard-universal-pictures-interview-news-1234699898/ |url-status=live |website=Deadline Hollywood |access-date=2021-04-06 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305023908/https://deadline.com/2021/02/news-of-the-world-composer-james-newton-howard-universal-pictures-interview-news-1234699898/ }}</ref>。

