er Bros. movies heading to HBO Max after 45-day theatrical window in 2022 |url=https://www.gamesradar.com/warner-bros-movies-heading-to-hbo-max-after-45-day-theatrical-window-in-2022/ |access-date=2021-10-31 |website=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |archive-date=2021-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210810092535/https://www.gamesradar.com/warner-bros-movies-heading-to-hbo-max-after-45-day-theatrical-window-in-2022/ |url-status=live }}</ref>。這部電影還以2D、[[IMAX|IMAX]]、[[杜比影院|杜比影院]]、[[4DX|4DX]]及{{le|ScreenX|ScreenX}}上發布<ref>{{Cite web |last=Dominguez |first=Noah |date=2022-03-21 |title=Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore Debuts Magical 4DX, ScreenX Posters (Exclusive) |url=https://www.cbr.com/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-4dx-screenx-posters/ |access-date=2022-04-12 |website=CBR.com |archive-date=2022-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220603180441/https://www.cbr.com/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-4dx-screenx-posters/ }}</ref>。

