== 反響 ==
=== 票房 ===
{{As of|2022|5|23}}，《怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密》在美國和加拿大的票房收入為8,600萬美元，在其他地區為2.77億美元，全球總票房收入為4.01億美元<ref name=BOM/><ref name="NUM" />。

在美國和加拿大，《怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密》於首映週末將在4,200家影院上映，預計首周票房約為4,000萬美元<ref>{{cite web |url= https://variety.com/2022/film/box-office/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-opening-weekend-prediction-1235231886/ |date= 2022-04-13 |access-date= 2022-04-14 |title= Box Office: ‘Fantastic Beasts 3’ Aims for $40 Million Domestic Debut |author= Rebecca Rubin |work= Variety |archive-date= 2022-04-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20220414104006/https://variety.com/2022/film/box-office/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-opening-weekend-prediction-1235231886/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficepro.com/long-range-box-office-forecast-fantastic-beasts-the-secrets-of-dumbledore-and-father-stu/|title=Long Range Box Office Forecast: ''Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore'' and ''Father Stu''|date=2022-03-18|first=Shawn|last=Robbins|website=[[Boxoffice_Pro|Boxoffice Pro]]|access-date=2022-03-24|archive-date=2022-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220318103831/https://www.boxofficepro.com/long-range-box-office-forecast-fantastic-beasts-the-secrets-of-dumbledore-and-father-stu/}}</ref>。第一天票房為2,000萬美元，而當中包括週四晚上的600萬美元<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://variety.com/2022/film/news/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-secrets-of-dumbledore-jk-rowling-thursday-previews-1235233379/amp/ |title = Box Office: 'Fantastic Beasts 3' Opens to $6 Million in Thursday Previews |work = Variety |author = Brett Lang |date = 2022-04-15 |accessdate = 2022-04-15 |archive-date = 2022-04-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220415155205/https://variety.com/2022/film/news/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-secrets-of-dumbledore-jk-rowling-thursday-previews-1235233379/amp/ }}</ref>。首周票房4,220萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2022W15/|title=Domestic 2022 Weekend 15|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|access-date=2022-04-19|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419173842/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2022W15/}}</ref>，票房當週第一名卻為全系列最低首映票房。<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-1235002928/|title=''Dumbledore'' Opens To $43M U.S., Lowest In ''Harry Potter'' Franchise; What Now For The J.K. Rowling IP? – Sunday AM Update|date=2022-04-17|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2022-04-17|archive-date=2022-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416224642/https://deadline.com/2022/04/box-office-fantastic-beasts-3-1235002928/}}</ref>。第二周末的票房暴跌，只剩1,400萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2022W16/|title=Domestic 2022 Weekend 16|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|access-date=2022-04-26|archive-date=2022-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426134921/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2022W16/}}</ref>，這是繼《[[哈利波特－死神的聖物2|哈利波特－死神的聖物2]]》後，第二個最差的次周末跌幅，可見2011年第二個周末下跌了72%<ref>{{Cite web|date=2022-04-24|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|title=''Bad Guys'' Proves Family Pics Still Work With $24M Debut; Making Sense Of ''Northman'' & ''Unbearable Weight'' Counterprogramming In Streaming Era – Sunday Update|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/box-office-northman-bad-guys-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent-1235007973/|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2022-04-25|archive-date=2022-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220425024652/https://deadline.com/2022/04/box-office-northman-bad-guys-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent-1235007973/}}</ref>。第三周北美票房繼續下探到830萬美元，第四周再砍半，只剩下395萬美元。

在美國和加拿大以外，《怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密》在首映周末從22個國際市場也只獲得5,690萬美元的收入。在德國，這部電影的$920萬美元首映票房<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-rrr-morbius-sonic-the-hedgehog-2-batman-global-international-box-office-1234998767/|title=''Sonic 2'' Speeds To $141M Global; ''Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets Of Dumbledore'' Uncovers $57M In Early Offshore Bow; ''RRR'' Roars To WW Milestone – International Box Office|date=2022-04-12|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2022-04-12|archive-date=2022-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220411194757/https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-rrr-morbius-sonic-the-hedgehog-2-batman-global-international-box-office-1234998767/}}</ref>。這部電影在第二個周末賺得$7,170萬美元，這包括在法國和墨西哥開畫的$710萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-sonic-kgf-yash-india-china-global-international-box-office-1235004648/|title=''Fantastic Beasts'' Reaches $150M Overseas; India's ''KGF'' Rocks $70M+ Global Start; ''Sonic'' Speeds To $232M WW – International Box Office|date=2022-04-17|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2022-04-18|archive-date=2022-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220417230149/https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-sonic-kgf-yash-india-china-global-international-box-office-1235004648/}}</ref>。電影於第三個國際開畫周末增加了$3,830萬美元的收入。{{As of|2022|4|24}}，這部電影的最大市場是德國（$2,330萬美元）、 日本（$2,230萬美元）、英國（$2,170萬美元）、中國（$1,750萬美元）和法國（$1,360萬美元）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-sonic-the-hedgehog-2-lost-city-kgf-china-global-international-box-office-1235008855/|title=''Fantastic Beasts 3'' & ''Sonic 2'' Near $300M Global, ''The Lost City'' Tops $100M – International Box Office|date=2022-04-24|first=Nancy|last=Tartaglione|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2022-04-24|archive-date=2022-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220424173853/https://deadline.com/2022/04/fantastic-beasts-secrets-of-dumbledore-sonic-the-hedgehog-2-lost-city-kgf-china-global-international-box-office-1235008855/}}</ref>。由於北美票房與評價過差，扣除成本與宣傳費用，以及各國代理商抽成後確定嚴重虧損，成為全系列第一部票房毒藥。

