=== 評價 ===
在[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]][[爛番茄|爛番茄]]中，電影根據228則評論，獲得46%的新鮮度，平均得分為5.4/10。該網站的評論家一致認為：「《怪獸與鄧不利多的秘密》避免了一些困擾其前作的陷阱，但缺乏了許多前作電影把觀眾帶進巫師世界的魔力<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes |id={{RT data|rtid|noprefix=y}} |type=m |title=Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore |access-date=2022-04-22}}{{cbignore}}{{RT data|edit}}</ref>。」[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根據49位影論人給了這部電影的[[加權平均數|加權平均分]]為47/100，表示「混合或平均評論」<ref>{{Cite Metacritic |id=fantastic-beasts-the-secrets-of-dumbledore |type=movie |title=Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore Reviews |accessdate=2022-04-15}}</ref><ref>{{Cite Metacritic|id=fantastic-beasts-the-secrets-of-dumbledore|type=movie|title=Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore|access-date=2022-04-08}}</ref>。

根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]的調查，觀眾從A+至F的評級中給予這部電影為「B+」，跟《[[怪獸與葛林戴華德之罪|怪獸與葛林戴華德之罪]]》並列整個[[魔法世界_(跨媒體製作)|跨媒體製作]]的最低評級；而《{{le|PostTrak|PostTrak}}》的那些人給予81%的好評，平均得分為4.2／5<ref>{{Cite Rotten Tomatoes|title=Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore|id=fantastic_beasts_the_secrets_of_dumbledore|type=movie|access-date=2022-04-08}}</ref>，他們當中的63%表示肯定會推薦此電影<ref name="opening" />。一些評論當中有一個特別重點就是讚揚麥斯·米基辛作為葛林戴華德的表現優於尊尼·特普<ref>{{Cite web |last=Sharf |first=Zack |date=2022-04-05 |title='Fantastic Beasts 3' Critics: Mads Mikkelsen Is Better Than Johnny Depp and 'Should've Been Cast From the Start' |url=https://variety.com/2022/film/news/mads-mikkelsen-fantastic-beasts-3-better-johnny-depp-1235225472/ |access-date=2022-04-09 |website=Variety |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409000906/https://variety.com/2022/film/news/mads-mikkelsen-fantastic-beasts-3-better-johnny-depp-1235225472/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=updated |first=Heidi Venable last |date=2022-04-07 |title=How Mads Mikkelsen's Grindelwald Compares To Johnny Depp, According To Critics Who've Seen Fantastic Beasts 3 |url=https://www.cinemablend.com/movies/how-mads-mikkelsens-grindelwald-compares-to-johnny-depp-according-to-critics-whove-seen-fantastic-beasts-3 |access-date=2022-04-09 |website=CINEMABLEND |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220409001218/https://www.cinemablend.com/movies/how-mads-mikkelsens-grindelwald-compares-to-johnny-depp-according-to-critics-whove-seen-fantastic-beasts-3 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Cooper |first=Leonie |date=2022-04-15 |title=Mads Mikkelsen says replacing Johnny Depp in Fantastic Beasts was 'chaotic' |url=https://news.yahoo.com/mads-mikkelsen-says-replacing-johnny-145228045.html |access-date=2022-04-15 |website=Yahoo News |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416014405/https://news.yahoo.com/mads-mikkelsen-says-replacing-johnny-145228045